## AGI NATURAL PROCESSING

You asked: "AGI can naturally process these as well can it not?"

**Yes, absolutely.** The architecture we designed is **modality-agnostic by design:**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     AGI PROCESSING UNIVERSALITY                              │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
